sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Application
    participant XPC as XPC Subsystem
    participant MTL as MTLCompilerService

    App->>XPC: Initialize (implicit)
    XPC->>MTL: Establish connection
    MTL-->>XPC: Connection ready

    Note over App: fork() called

    App->>App: Parent exits
    App->>App: Child continues

    Note over App,XPC: XPC connection now invalid in child

    App->>XPC: Create render pipeline
    XPC->>MTL: Compile shader request
    MTL--xXPC: Connection invalid
    XPC-->>App: Error 3 - No such process
